msgid "New Invoice on %website_url."
msgstr "Сформирован новый счет на сайте %website_url."

#: libs/theme-setup.php:1361
msgid ""
"Hi there,\n"
"An invoice was generated for your booking request on %website_url !  A "
"deposit will be required for booking to be confirmed. For more details check "
"out your account, My Reservations page."
msgstr ""
"Здравствуйте!\n"
